{"tid":1140091,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump says tariffs on Chinese will increase to 25% on Friday","createTime":"2019-05-05T16:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T06:42:40.000Z","uid":76310,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"a1931dd5e81befdc66c83227d5701f7158596761","tid":1140091,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"Trump says tariffs on Chinese goods will increase to 25% on Friday<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/05/05/trump-says-tariffs-on-200-billion-of-chinese-goods-will-increase-to-25percent-on-friday.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2019%2F05%2F05%2Ftrump-says-tariffs-on-200-billion-of-chinese-goods-will-increase-to-25percent-on-friday.html&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=a3ce96ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2019/05/05/trump-says-tariffs-on-200-billion-of-chinese-goods-will-increase-to-25percent-on-friday.html</a><br />\n<br />\nPresident Donald Trump said that tariffs on $200 billion of Chinese goods will increase to 25% on Sunday, despite repeated claims by the administration that trade talks with Beijing were going well. <br />\n<br />\nThe tariff rate on those goods was originally set at 10%. Trump had originally threatened to increase the tariffs at the start of the year, but postponed that decision after China and the US agreed to sit down for trade talks.<br />\n<br />\nIn addition, Trump threatened impose 25% tariffs on an additional $325 billion of Chinese goods &ldquo;shortly.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\nOn Friday, Vice President Mike Pence told CNBC that Trump remained hopeful that he could strike a deal with China. <br />\n<br />\nChinese President Xi Jinping and U.S. President Donald Trump attend a welcome ceremony at the Great Hall of the People in Beijing on November 9, 2017.<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/105280924-GettyImages-871867102.jpg?v=1553014154&amp;w=740&amp;h=492\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cnbcfm.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fimage%2F105280924-GettyImages-871867102.jpg%3Fv%3D1553014154%26w%3D740%26h%3D492&h=7806dc25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5942cea4aadb6006f36b3004ec843d545e19345","tid":1140091,"uid":22839,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"五窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真支爆"},{"pid":"f34b10abe9f8c70a2e28ed5d0f49836c32ed8c3b","tid":1140091,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8f56dc06aee773aec25a20bfe56e19f0b18696","tid":1140091,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f34b10abe9f8c70a2e28ed5d0f49836c32ed8c3b","tid":1140091,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"增加內需就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de5705538efa75c40cac4e40ad12e906d7d9686","tid":1140091,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"跌市了"},{"pid":"ebf0f40f22925d2d72a445601e15c6374be95d79","tid":1140091,"uid":20368,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<br />\n又搞鳩d股<br />\n你地咁開心做咩？<br />\n無貨？"},{"pid":"43e709514fe580d1942f27c6fe38a23645bd2cec","tid":1140091,"uid":24805,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ebf0f40f22925d2d72a445601e15c6374be95d79","tid":1140091,"uid":20368,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<br />\n又搞鳩d股<br />\n你地咁開心做咩？<br />\n無貨？"},"c